<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="18May1920"><font color="red">18 May 1920</font>, <cite>Yale</cite> (JJ to Ezra Pound): The <cite>Oxen of the Sun</cite> episode is finished but the typing is still a job. As soon as it is ready will post you express to be sent on to New York and to Miss Weaver as it is overdue &hellip; <cite>Ulysses</cite> leaves me no time for sleep much less for other work &hellip; This episode has cost me about a thousand hours of work. Thank the lord it is finished &hellip; I shall get on with the typing as quickly as possible and send off the script.</div>
